!!! 5
%html
  %head
    %meta{charset:"utf-8"}
    / Always force latest IE rendering engine or request Chrome Frame
    %meta{content: "IE=edge,chrome=1", http:{equiv:"X-UA-Compatible"}}
    
    %title The Impermenant Marker
    
    %link{:href => "http://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Raleway:100,200,400,700", :rel => "stylesheet", :type => "text/css"}
    = stylesheet_link_tag "all"
    = javascript_include_tag  "all"
  
  %body{class:page_classes}
    %main.container
      %header
        .clearfix
          .issue-number.right
            %span.unit No.
            %var 0
        %h1 
          %span.small the
          Impermanent Marker
        %hr.thin
        %h2.mission
          Short-form temporary writing on the ephemeral and obsolescent. Exploring impermanence one piece at a time.

      %hr.thick

      %article
        %header 
        = yield

      %hr.thick

      / TODO:
      / %section.past-authors

    %footer.dark-color
      .container
        %hr.thick
        %ul.list-unstyled.list-inline
          %li
            %a{href:"mailto:delete@impermanentmarker.com"} Contact
          %li
            %a{href:"/archive.html", data:{modal:"#archive-modal"}} Archive
          %li            
            %a{href:"/faq.html"} FAQ
        %p
          Interested in writing for the impermanent marker? 
          %a{href:"mailto:delete@impermanentmarker.com"} Drop us a line